| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2725 — Recovery Inhibition (werewolves)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 719d3efe-b7be-54a5-8fa5-01c1719dbaf5"
